<div class="container">
    <h1>Return Policy</h1>

    <div class="return-policy">
        <p>Our Return Policy allows you to request a refund for your hotel reservations under certain conditions. Please take note of the following terms and conditions:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>- All refund requests must be made within 24 hours of making the reservation.</li>
            <li>- Refunds are only applicable for reservations that have not been used or checked-in.</li>
            <li>- A processing fee of 10% will be deducted from the refund amount.</li>
            <li>- Refunds will be processed within 7-10 business days after the request is approved.</li>
            <li>- For refund requests, please contact our customer support team with your reservation details.</li>
            <li>- Refunds are subject to the terms and conditions outlined in our Refund Policy document.</li>
            <li>- Refunds for cancellations made less than 48 hours before the check-in date are not eligible.</li>
            <li>- Refunds are issued to the original payment method used for the reservation.</li>
            <li>- No-shows and early check-outs are not eligible for refunds.</li>
            <li>- Refunds are processed in the currency of the original reservation.</li>
            <li>- Refunds for reservations made during special promotions may be subject to different terms.</li>
            <li>- Refunds for group bookings are handled on a case-by-case basis.</li>
            <li>- Refunds for reservations made through third-party platforms may have different refund policies.</li>
            <li>- Refunds for reservations affected by natural disasters or unforeseen circumstances are evaluated individually.</li>
            <li>- Refunds are not provided for changes in travel plans or personal preferences.</li>
            <li>- Refunds are not applicable to non-refundable or prepaid reservations.</li>
            <li>- Partial refunds may be offered for early departures or shortened stays.</li>
            <li>- Refunds for optional add-ons or extras are determined by their respective cancellation policies.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>- If you have any further questions or need assistance regarding our Return Policy, please don't hesitate to reach out to our customer support team. We're here to help!</p>
    </div>
